{
  "texts": [
    "We test the range of 𝑘 from 0.2 to 0.8, incrementing by 0.1, and report the metacognitive proportion and answer quality on 2WikiMultihopQA.",
    "MethodAs depicted in Figure 4(a), when the threshold is set to 0.2, roughly 15% of questions are directed to the evaluator-critic LLM for metacognitive reasoning (green bars).",
    "At this point, there is approximately a 20% improvement compared to Reflexion.",
    "As the threshold increases, the proportion of questions requiring metacognitive reasoning steadily increases.",
    "By the time the threshold reaches 0.8, this arrives to 84%."
  ]
}